# Gradle wrapper artifacts (gradlew, gradlew.bat, gradle-wrapper.jar) are
# intentionally tracked so contributors and CI can build the project
# without installing Gradle separately. The wrapper properties live under
# gradle/wrapper/gradle-wrapper.properties and are also committed.

